a sinc with circular symmetry.

00:39:53.090 --> 00:39:55.780
It is not exactly a sinc.

00:39:55.780 --> 00:39:58.840
It is given by a rather
nasty formula here.

00:39:58.840 --> 00:40:00.640
It is the ratio.

00:40:00.640 --> 00:40:03.270
First of all, it is all
