energy conservation.

00:57:12.340 --> 00:57:15.280
It relates the modulus--

00:57:15.280 --> 00:57:18.810
the integral of the
modulus of a function.

00:57:18.810 --> 00:57:20.270
We recognize this as energy.

00:57:20.270 --> 00:57:23.350
